title: Combat Arms Online FPS from Nexon
description: Awesome new first person shooter from nexon. Like COD4 and Counter-strike but better in my opinion. More realistic weapons, ranking, faster game play, better maps and better money system, and completely customizable characters. The only downside said by some is that there is no voice coms but its ok with me because i have no mic and I hate mic spammers anyway. This game is 100% free but you do have to register on nexon's site. I give this game a 9.1 out of 10, it deserves a game of the year award. SEED! :-)
